<A>__{suburban connecticut, outside of new york city, 1973. the still after a terrible storm. trees dripping, their branches torn, the air warming just before the break of a new day. the train lies dark and motionless, a few flashing yellow emergency lights up front, as a work crew removes debris from the track.}
